high_descs: Walk to the kitchen island behind you.
Grab a sponge off the island.
Walk to the kitchen sink on your right.
Put the sponge in the sink, wash it, then grab it again.
Walk to the kitchen shelf next to the counter.
Put the sponge on the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Clean a sponge and store it in a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the center of the island, turn right to face the island.
Pick up the green sponge on the island.
Bring the sponge to the sink behind you to the right.
Clean the sponge in the sink with water.
Bring the cleaned sponge back to the wooden shelf behind you and to the right, past the counter.
Stand the sponge on the middle shelf, in front of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Stand a cleaned sponge on the middle shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then turn right to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the sponge off of the island.
Turn right and walk over to the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn off the water and remove the now clean sponge.
Turn around and across the room, then turn right to face the wooden shelving unit to the left of the counter.
Put the clean sponge on the front right edge of the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on a shelf.
